secubox-nettweak (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release - Network tuning module.
  * FastAPI backend with sysctl management.
  * Endpoints: status, profiles, tcp, net, apply, reload.
  * Tuning profiles: default, performance, low-latency, security, router.
  * Configuration persistence via sysctl.d.
  * P31 Phosphor light theme frontend.
  * Tabs: Overview, TCP Settings, Network Settings, Profiles.

